<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Verification Failed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      max-width: 400px;
      width: 90%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .icon {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #e63946;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    ul {
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: #e63946;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #d62839;
    }

    .support {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    .support a {
      color: #e63946;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">❌</div>
    <h1>Verification Failed</h1>
    <p>We couldn't verify your request due to a reCAPTCHA error.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Incomplete reCAPTCHA challenge</li>
      <li>Session timeout</li>
      <li>Network issues</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/api/v.01/verify?token=${encodeURIComponent(token)}" class="btn">Try Again</a>
    <p class="support">Still need help? <a href="mailto:amankumar78277@gmail.com">Contact support</a></p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
